metadata.name: The Fruit War 1
metadata.description:
EDITION 1 OF 1  

Collection: The Fruit Wars  
Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2021  
Minted: 2022. 

The Fruit Wars is a collection of 100 unique abstract paintings which explore variations in color, 3D shapes & explore graphic design to make it look like generative art using automation. The collection evolves to modern work exploring abstraction by connecting & layering colored cubes to resemble a pixel per box in a signature design that Godwits created.  

Published by: Abstract Art Labs  
Contract By: Manifold Studios  
Contract Type: ERC-721  
Artist Royalty: 7.5%.
